调节其运动，直到到达最终目的地。这种蛋白质可以引导神经元通过相互排斥的分子途径迁移并确定神经细胞的方向。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-protein-directs-neuronal-migration-in-the-embryonic-brain2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 13:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/a-protein-directs-neuronal-migration-in-the-embryonic-brain</guid></item><item><title>使用多基因面板精确诊断威尔逊病前瞻性队列研究的见解</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/precision-diagnosis-of-wilson-disease-using-a-multigene-panelinsights-from-a-prospective-cohort-study</link><description>该网站使用安全服务来防范恶意机器人。当网站验证您不是机器人时会显示此页面。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/precision-diagnosis-of-wilson-disease-using-a-multigene-panelinsights-from-a-prospective-cohort-study.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 13:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/precision-diagnosis-of-wilson-disease-using-a-multigene-panelinsights-from-a-prospective-cohort-study</guid></item><item><title>母胎界面作为免疫屏障：结构、调节和分解</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-maternal-fetal-interface-as-an-immunological-barrier-structure-regulation-and-breakdown</link><description>母胎界面是一种特殊的免疫屏障，在整个妊娠过程中整合了耐受、防御和调节炎症。不同的免疫群体介导着床、免疫稳态和分娩，而失调可能导致慢性胎盘炎症，这是屏障失效的结果，其特征是母体 T 细胞浸润到胎盘/胎儿组织。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-maternal-fetal-interface-as-an-immunological-barrier-structure-regulation-and-breakdown2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 13:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-maternal-fetal-interface-as-an-immunological-barrier-structure-regulation-and-breakdown</guid></item><item><title>高斯泼溅是我最喜欢的东西，所以我请一位前 Epic 艺术家告诉我他所知道的关于低成本“照片真实”渲染技术的一切</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/gaussian-splatting-is-my-new-favourite-thing-so-i-hassled-an-ex-epic-artist-to-tell-me-everything-he-knows-about-the-low-cost-photo-real-rendering-technique</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 12:53:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/gaussian-splatting-is-my-new-favourite-thing-so-i-hassled-an-ex-epic-artist-to-tell-me-everything-he-knows-about-the-low-cost-photo-real-rendering-technique</guid></item><item><title>光遗传学介导的收缩性能够可逆控制体内小胶质细胞的形态和迁移</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/optogenetic-mediated-contractility-enables-reversible-control-of-microglial-morphology-and-migration-in-vivo</link><description>比尔迈尔等人。使用斑马鱼的实时成像显示小胶质细胞在支持大脑监视和吞噬作用的不同形态状态之间交替。通过光遗传学控制细胞骨架收缩性，他们展示了对活体大脑中小胶质细胞行为的可编程、可逆控制。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/optogenetic-mediated-contractility-enables-reversible-control-of-microglial-morphology-and-migration-in-vivo.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 12:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/optogenetic-mediated-contractility-enables-reversible-control-of-microglial-morphology-and-migration-in-vivo</guid></item><item><title>“我们能在科技中生存吗？”作者：约翰·冯·诺依曼</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/can-we-survive-technology-by-john-von-neumann</link><description>这是一篇由&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-we-survive-technology-by-john-von-neumann2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 01:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/can-we-survive-technology-by-john-von-neumann</guid></item><item><title>量子通信的良好振动：工程师将单个声子耦合到单个原子自旋</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/good-vibrations-for-quantum-communications-engineers-couple-single-phonon-to-single-atomic-spin</link><description>哈佛大学约翰·A·保尔森工程与应用科学学院 (SEAS) 的研究人员首次证明了单个振动能量量子与单个原子自旋相互作用，为使用声音而不是光或电作为信息载体的量子技术奠定了基础。结果发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/good-vibrations-for-quantum-communications-engineers-couple-single-phonon-to-single-atomic-spin.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 01:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/good-vibrations-for-quantum-communications-engineers-couple-single-phonon-to-single-atomic-spin</guid></item></channel></rss>